profile: Easy Eaves Home Improvements is a locally owned business in the Dawson Creek area specializing in residential, commercial and industrial construction, locally owned and operated we are dedicated to quality workmanship. We offer a wide range of services, we can do it all when it comes to your construction needs. We have the knowledge, skill and creativity necessary to complete any job big or small, on time and on budget. Individuals wanting to custom build the home of their dreams or renovate their existing dwelling have came to the right place. Easy Eaves Home Improvements is licenced and insured to give you peace of mind. A consultation to start planning your next construction project is just a phone call away!
